{"tid":2308881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登：不會立即取消與中國首階段關稅協議","createTime":"2020-12-02T07:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T02:02:16.000Z","uid":278587,"like":8,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a696933ffc26ec28a13b167b0b64f688707990","tid":2308881,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:45:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=415085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415085&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2YR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=056e904b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415085&h=0e3a6486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=415085</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國總統當選人拜登表示，不會馬上取消中國首階段關稅協議。<br />\n<br />\n拜登接受《紐約時報》專欄作者訪問時表示，他會保留現任總統特朗普今年初，與中國達成的首階段貿易協議，即維持對中國出口美國商品徵收兩成半關稅的決定。<br />\n<br />\n拜登表示，首先會對與中國達成的協議進行全面檢視，亦會與亞洲及歐洲的傳統盟友磋商，才制定連貫的對華政策。<br />\n<br />\n拜登認為，對華戰略的最佳做法，是令美國每一個盟友或者是曾經的盟友站在同一立場。拜登稱，他就職後的數個星期，優先要做的是與盟友統一立場。"},{"pid":"72d53c2941809aceab9eedba3c1bd5bdc5a9eb75","tid":2308881,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:46:36.000Z","msg":"春袋被夾"},{"pid":"79ca3e48b3ea43121fb137dd43599b6593552df1","tid":2308881,"uid":18569,"like":37,"dislike":5,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"你撚係總統咩，關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b1b5a1ab39b51ccc46305ca1fbe9bed460c0ad","tid":2308881,"uid":67468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a364899b215a8c52eb12f55ca0ff0d9cd520329a","tid":2308881,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/l